overview: The 2019 Dream Concert kicked off on May 18 at the Seoul World Cup Stadium.  The lineup of performers this year included SHINee’s Taemin, AB6IX, Red Velvet, SEVENTEEN, NCT DREAM, INFINITE’s Nam Woohyun, BTOB’s Ilhoon, MAMAMOO, HOTSHOT’s Ha Sung Woon, Oh My Girl, CLC, The Boyz, DIA, Golden Child, Kim Dong Han, N.Flying, JBJ95, (G)I-DLE, TRCNG, 1THE9, Kim Tae Woo, Park Bom, Hong Jin Young, and Clon.  The MCs for the night were actress Jun So Min, Super Junior’s Leeteuk, and B1A4’s Gongchan.
title: 2019 Dream Concert
